    [1] = workspace.NPCFolder.Temple.Humanoid, -- Doflamingo, Teach, Crocodile, Grimmjow, Szayelaporro, Medazeppi, Yahaba, Kaidou, Susamaru, Ulquiorra Cifer, Sakazuki, Sōsuke (no idea if this one works), Temple, Akaza
